PDATE CPU配合佢用又可以更快, 連FACEID 個硬件都冇更新過......<br />\n<br />\nM字額係難頂, 但係取捨之下, 有佢解鎖同做交易, 係放心好多"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"Face ID真心好用，又快又準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:30:57.000Z","msg":"pixel 4 嗰個呢咁"},{"pid":"44806b3a3ac5a3c88c959582bce729768fbb56b6","tid":1785262,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:31:59.000Z","msg":"試下用習種個樣唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11e20a3e3a8ce2c846861697194568fab2da679","tid":1785262,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa849098a074414c4a6a02d312393a4b16c6302","tid":1785262,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a72cb88be657dc446692e88702d1783dae6fe8e2","tid":1785262,"uid":74302,"like":33,"dislike":6,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"192916738202cd3dff2a4d831fe789e4e79e0bc6","tid":1785262,"uid":158499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"Haters成日話Apple啲機廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"事實係FACE ID 可能係APPLE 近年推出最完美既技術<br />\n因為一出就好精準，冇BUG，只有愈來愈快......硬件唔洗提升都會加快<br />\n而單純新機UPDATE CPU配合佢用又可以更快, 連FACEID 個硬件都冇更新過......<br />\n<br />\nM字額係難頂, 但係取捨之下, 有佢解鎖同做交易, 係放心好多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:37:27.000Z","msg":"pixel 4 無 m 額，點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/24183038/2019-10-24-14.00.53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F24183038%2F2019-10-24-14.00.53.png&h=ce816ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPixel 4 另外一個新功能，其實是 3D 臉部解鎖功能，Google 稱它為 Face Unlock。與以往 Android 手機的 2D 臉部解鎖不同，Pixel 4 在手機螢幕上方設計了紅外線照射器、紅外線微點投影器以及紅外線相機，因此可透過偵測臉部 3D 曲線而達到更高的臉部解鎖安全性，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原理與 iPhone 的 Face ID 基本上是一樣的</strong></span>，因此在行動支付時，也可以透過 Face Unlock 來做為身分驗證。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，Pixel 4 的 Face Unlock 也與 Motion Sense 互相合作，前面提到當 Motion Sense 偵測到有人在附近時，會把螢幕 AOD 打開，這時只要在螢幕上方揮一下手，鎖定畫面就會開啟，然後再把臉湊過去，手機就自動解鎖，從頭到尾都不需要碰到手機。另外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Face Unlock 不論是直立、橫向或是上下顛倒，怎麼拿手機都可以解鎖，這點與 iPhone 只能直立解鎖相比方便很多。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"97828c01555506e77f8d9fcc0f704ad3fec072a0","tid":1785262,"uid":133375,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fe2afc720252edb6231ed78864ce8d28bccb1515","tid":1785262,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a72cb88be657dc446692e88702d1783dae6fe8e2","tid":1785262,"uid":74302,"like":33,"dislike":6,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"192916738202cd3dff2a4d831fe789e4e79e0bc6","tid":1785262,"uid":158499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"Haters成日話Apple啲機廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"事實係FACE ID 可能係APPLE 近年推出最完美既技術<br />\n因為一出就好精準，冇BUG，只有愈來愈快......硬件唔洗提升都會加快<br />\n而單純新機UPDATE CPU配合佢用又可以更快, 連FACEID 個硬件都冇更新過......<br />\n<br />\nM字額係難頂, 但係取捨之下, 有佢解鎖同做交易, 係放心好多"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"Face ID真心好用，又快又準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:50:43.000Z","msg":"d an狗話an機未對塊面已經unlock到<br />\n我笑到仆街"},{"pid":"2310daff525ee72afad3fc14a76d8a6cd6fd4d2e","tid":1785262,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:53:22.000Z","msg":"金田一時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00778bb86e96c6163db2ec1bd0e44dd849f2850","tid":1785262,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:55:14.000Z","msg":"重要！大家要小心「e肚仔」呢個app！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786046</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b54e8ced0d37bc6d2e37efed068b1bda5a6c39e","tid":1785262,"uid":263198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"Face ID 係咪唔包瞳孔驗證？"},{"pid":"5f438db665f714b30a57da96b05cb997fe1aef1c","tid":1785262,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:20:42.000Z","msg":"可以大搞，經濟入侵"},{"pid":"95d79f6609b26a14cc36e4fdf40b3b87e181eded","tid":1785262,"uid":174063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"204f7c4a481441cb6e2822aa1c42deb87fd7f10d","tid":1785262,"uid":25797,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"個個印藍屍黑警樣去示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0nxA4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0nxA4j.jpg&h=4e822fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甘樣得吾得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c0c147e3345d85b03f17a024298138a6ffc860","tid":1785262,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3a1654aa38fcd0ec0fb78e6e17a3a8426c7e1b","tid":1785262,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"美AI公司用3D面具 騙過微信及支付寶人臉識別<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2520888/%E7%BE%8EAI%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%A83D%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%B7%20%E9%A8%99%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%AF%B6%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2520888%2F%25E7%25BE%258EAI%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2594%25A83D%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%2585%25B7%2520%25E9%25A8%2599%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%2589%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%2588%25A5&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=694e4e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2520888/%E7%BE%8EAI%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%A83D%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%B7%20%E9%A8%99%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%AF%B6%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n戴上人臉面具蒙混闖關，是電影《職業特攻隊（Mission: Impossible）》中的情節，如今在現實中竟也成真。一家位於美國加州的人工智能（AI）技術公司宣稱，成功使用3D面具欺騙支付寶、微信等中國支付軟件中的人臉識別系統，甚至以手機螢幕上的照片，在荷蘭最大的機場通過人臉識別驗證登機。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞報道，這家叫做耐能智慧（Kneron）的人工智能公司成立於2015年，總部位於美國加州聖地亞哥市。公司的主營業務是提供人工智能物聯網（AIoT）、智能家居、智能監控能軟硬體解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n美國「財富（Fortune）」網站報道，Kneron近期開展一項測試，嘗試欺騙公共場所和支付系統的人臉識別系統。在亞洲，他們的團隊在商場中使用高質量的3D面具，成功欺騙了支付寶（Alipay）和微信的支付（WeChat Pay）程式，進行購物付款。<br />\n<br />\n更令人擔心的，是Kneron在部分交通樞紐地點所做的實驗。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Kneron團隊在自助登機的荷蘭最大機場&mdash;&mdash;阿姆斯特丹史基普機場（Schiphol Airport），僅用手機螢幕上的照片，就騙過感應器。它也能夠以此進入中國的火車站，據了解，目前的中國通勤族能使用臉部辨識支付車費並上下火車。</span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n人臉識別非百份百安全 或存恐襲、詐騙風險</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國科技媒體The verge表示，他們獲得了Kneron的測試視頻。視頻中，測試人員戴著3D面具通過人臉識別測試，登錄中國商店裡的支付寶和微信支付終端，被允許購買。另一短片，同一位戴著面具的測試人員將身分證放到火車站閘門，閘門上的面部識別系統將面具當成他的臉。應Kneron要求，上述測試視頻未被公開。<br />\n<br />\nThe verge特別提到，暫時還不需擔心他人製作你的人臉面具進行消費，因為上述測試具有局限性。目前的視頻信息僅顯示一個人嘗試使用面具進行操作，還不清楚這個面具是否每次嘗試均有效，以及其他面具是否也能通過這些（人臉識別）測試。<br />\n<br />\n儘管The verge這樣說，但目前正當各國安全單位使用臉部辨識功能作為省時省錢的措施，這些交通實驗結果畢，竟會引發恐怖攻擊的疑慮；而<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在支付平台的案例中，能用口罩騙過微信支付及支付寶的Kneron，也引發詐騙及身分竊取的擔憂。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n事實上，Kneron旅美台裔創辦人兼執行長劉峻誠表示：「這顯示偽裝成人工智能的次等臉部辨識科技，會讓用戶隱私權受到威脅；雖然也有解決這些問題的科技存在，但各企業並未更新技術。這些企業走的是捷徑，犧牲了安全。」但<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Kneron補充，他們的實驗無法騙過一些臉部辨識程式，特別是蘋果公司（Apple）的智能手機iPhone X。</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:25:50.000Z","msg":"明要玩尻共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f128ab390492722cbb4d2e5eb39c6a159f7f7e23","tid":1785262,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:26:43.000Z","msg":"自煮研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7270f54b41bd4036186863c9a5cb2e873c5e8f","tid":1785262,"uid":14399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204f7c4a481441cb6e2822aa1c42deb87fd7f10d","tid":1785262,"uid":25797,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"個個印藍屍黑警樣去示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70f3ea88e55935ef05edf24274e52a91157a0bc","tid":1785262,"uid":26591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"靜靜地.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595a9fd262598ea31235d92d698fc1086992da1a","tid":1785262,"uid":281227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"6bd34e94f5dbaee77108278165593b4ca8bc81da","tid":1785262,"uid":254110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:39:30.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦<br />\n大陸人都係用iphone<br />\n再者中共拎錢又唔洗破解face id"},{"pid":"4721629710abd8110329718731c7a5a3bd9f5e39","tid":1785262,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd475a1a42e61ee564104af01d2189fada670b04","tid":1785262,"uid":